# Toggle Component Rule

The [Toggle.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Toggle.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- Single File Component (SFC) in `src/components/ui`.
- Used for toggling between on/off states (switch UI).
- Accepts `active` (boolean, default: false) and `size` (`small` | `large`, default: `large`) props.
- Emits a `change` event when toggled.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.
- Accessible: uses `role="switch"` and `aria-checked` attributes.

For toggle best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Switch documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/switch) as a reference.





